BT5511 code repository
Cell viability, RNA and Protein analysis file provides the code used to determine which genes significantly increased or decreased Cell viability, RNA expression or Protein expression levels.
The Anap7c1 file provides the code used to identify the mutations and types of mutations present in the Anap7c1 gene. 
The Avon4 file provides the code used to identify the mutations and types of mutations present in the Avon4 gene. 
The Dsgt9a1 file provides the code used to identify the mutations and types of mutations present in the Dsgt9a1 gene.
The Ist9a2 file provides the code used to identify the mutations and types of mutations present in the Ist9a2 gene. 
The Nect1c1 file provides the code used to identify the mutations and types of mutations present in the Nect1c1 gene.
